{"tid":1645723,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 如果我係林鄭，我下一步棋係...","createTime":"2019-10-11T03:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:05:27.000Z","uid":331650,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e43cd944c323f5f0d8b2e944db964971c9a6c21","tid":1645723,"uid":331650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:53:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鼓勵你地開花，</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但今次製造一個更大既意外，如假示威者打死黑警</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>，令人權法過唔到</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n分析如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>黨鐵停既時間</ins></span></span><br />\n平日8pm 停，六日全日停，然後今日變10pm停，之前四個月都唔停，十一前都未試過平日停。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">可能性有三: </span></span><br />\na) 製造早停=社會平靜冇示威現象=令你覺得佢想用黎停你示威，令你覺得運動熱度減退，好想出黎開花，然後<ins>係美國過人權法前</ins>出現標題講既事件--出現假示威者打死一個popo，令外國無法插手。<br />\n<br />\nb) 裝左唔知咩野入地鐵，製造假示威者造成意外 &gt; 整死/大量popo傷亡事件 (如荔景站，紅墈站出軌事件話我地知，要出事係好易)。而呢排停既時間係用黎做研究點做到b點。<br />\n<br />\nc) 承上，不排除在全面裝人面識別系統。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. <ins>見到好多風吹緊謝sir篤灰，黑警就黎頂唔順 (鳩硬sir果d)，</ins><strong><ins>令你輕敵。[</ins></strong>red]不要忘記佢地同港共永遠係最狡猾果個![/red]。不要成日覺得自己就贏。仲有篤灰個證據呢? 真係FC左? 用咩方法FC? 呢個都係睇post者要思考既問題! <span style=\"color: red;\">未真FC前，永不要當真!</span> 矛頭永遠指番去政權!<br />\n<br />\n對應方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">短暫性改變維持熱度方法:</span></span><br />\nEg. 和里非唱歌連儂快閃0破壞集會<br />\n係短暫姐，等到過人權法之後再決定咪得囉。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">心態改變#</span>[/size=5][/size=5]</strong>[/u][/u]</span>bye#pig<br />\n記住今次係一場<ins>抗爭</ins>，非<ins>比賽定輸贏</ins>，比賽會係限定時間完，抗爭不會。<br />\n抗爭係世代在角力，永無完結之日。<br />\n<br />\n解散警隊，刻不容緩。<br />\n香港人，反抗!"},{"pid":"2b98880f4dd8e62a5ad16667443de52f7cc11e1c","tid":1645723,"uid":181065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2a401a19e13158d83eee52ecc057bb85b30a169","tid":1645723,"uid":262966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf57dab9f84209cf6c95793f3ff1e391dcf1abfd","tid":1645723,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf063c5bed7af044a57a90b47937701bde469e8b","tid":1645723,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:05:23.000Z","msg":"切勿輕敵 <br />\n對家成個中共係背後<br />\n點會無棋 講無棋個d都On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa081ba34e4d5f77df28defb4c608bdbc4cd2d17","tid":1645723,"uid":157042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"好彩你唔係林鄭，咁到比你諗到條咁既橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd25164cc601da641dcd694e3c4e0c2580f03fa","tid":1645723,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:06:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8450e9259b2f710795a0ed18f93f48f45cdc2f27","tid":1645723,"uid":309873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"不推文。<br />\n<br />\n有事發生 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">引致</span> 人權法過唔到<br />\n呢個推論係毫無根據。而且港共要殺差佬真係唔需要係示威對陣時殺，伏擊殺黎引輿論一樣得，同示威與否無關，所以推論去轉活動完全不合理。<br />\n<br />\n我唔反對轉形式，只係想講此POST數個推論都係不符邏輯既。"},{"pid":"3728c546885a71bd9a7fb31bcd5f5ca2c894828c","tid":1645723,"uid":331650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8450e9259b2f710795a0ed18f93f48f45cdc2f27","tid":1645723,"uid":309873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s